They found out about it and they were upset.... AT EACH OTHER! They both still get along fine with the guy, but will no longer speak to each other. WTF?<br>
<br>
All 3 of these people are friends of mine and I get along fine with them all, but why in the hell do these women act like it's the fault of the other woman when they both know and have admitted that it's the guy that was lying?<br>
<br>
It's one thing if women don't mind being with a lying womanizer (while ignoring other guys of course), but it's a little much when they blame other women for it. <br>
